title: FRIDAY - Week 9 Aaron Rodgers and Davante Adams shine 2020
itunes:title: FRIDAY - Week 9 Aaron Rodgers and Davante Adams shine 2020
description:
Week 9 kicked off in a matchup between the Packers and 49ers (0:06) as Aaron Rodgers and Davante Adams shine for Green Bay in the win. Sunday will pit two of the league's rising stars at QB (0:47) as Miami's Tua Tagovailoa faces off against Arizona's Kyler Murray. Christian McCaffrey (2:36) set to make his return and we'll hear what Patrick Mahomes has to say about the Panthers running back. Plus, the Raiders hit with some fines due to their handling of a COVID-19 case with one of their players
